Problem 4

avg.imp <- function(a,avg) {
  missing <- is.na(a)
  imputed <- a
  imputed[missing] <- avg
  return (imputed)
}
wine_df_imputed$RS <- avg.imp(wine_df$RS, mean(wine_df$RS, na.rm = TRUE))
mean(wine_df_imputed$RS)
